The testbench code includes the modules stimulus_gen and tb. stimulus_gen has tasks for wavedrom and reset testing. The tb module instantiates the DUT (TopModule), golden model (RefModule), and stimulus. It uses posedge/negedge clk to check mismatches, tracks errors, and displays the result. The queue for mismatch display uses input_queue, got_queue, golden_queue, and reset_queue. Mismatch detection triggers display of the first error. Also includes timeout handling. Signal widths and assignments are as per the original code, with logic types where needed.